document_data.name: Woodside Way
document_data.mainbody: '''Woodside Way''' was a small avenue found in the city of [[Westgate]].
document_data.Location: Woodside way was located in the south section of the city. It branched from [[Silverpiece Way]] and met with [[Westgate Market Street]] near the [[Lord's Water]] pool. Several prominent castles were found along Woodside Way.
